#: faq.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "<!-- ## Do I really need to include the license and copyright headers in all files? Why should I care? {#why-care}\n"
msgstr ""
"<!-- ## ¿Realmente necesito incluir las cabeceras de licencia y copyright en "
